<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Closes Lower </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, December 20 (Xinhua) -- The general price index on
Tehran Stock Exchange Monday closed at 1,535.16, down 11.21
points from Sunday's finish.
</P>
<P>
A total of 33,978,457 shares changed hands in 776 turns and the
turnover reached over 11 billion rials (about 18.4 million
U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The shares of eight manufacturing units made gains while those
of 24 others declined. 
</P>
