<HEADLINE> mee122119hke - Netanyahu Expounds Peace Policy in Crucial </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JERUSALEM, December 21 (Xinhua) -- At a crucial meeting of the
Israeli Knesset (parliament) on Monday, Prime Minister Benjamin
Netanyahu Monday expounded his policy in the peace talks with the
Palestinians.
</P>
<P>
The plenum of the Knesset, which opened Monday afternoon, is
due to vote later on a bill calling for dissolution of the
Knesset and early elections.
</P>
