territories to the Palestinians in the first phase of the
withdrawal according to the Wye peace accord signed with the
Palestinians two months ago.
</P>
<P>
But, he said, the Palestinian National Authority failed to
fulfill its commitments to fight terrorism and avoid unilateral
activities.
</P>
<P>
Netanyahu reiterated his conditions to further implement the
agreement, which were approved by the Israeli cabinet on
Sunday.
