<HEADLINE> Istanbul Stock Exchange Stock Index Closes Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, December 21 (Xinhua) -- Turkey's Istanbul Stock
Exchange National-100 Index closed at 2,418.60 on Monday, up
78.92 points, or 3.37 percent, from Friday's finish.
</P>
