<HEADLINE> Deutsche Bank Expansion Continues </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BONN, December 21 (Xinhua) -- Deutsche Bank AG is continuing
its expansion with announcing a 10 per cent buy-in at the
second-biggest bank in Greece, EFG Eurobank.
</P>
<P>
A spokesman of the Deutsche Bank noted Monday that following
takeovers in Italy, Spain, and a few weeks ago in Belgium, the new
venture was a further step in Deutsche Bank's expansion in Europe
in what is the German bank's first-ever such move in Greece.
</P>
