<HEADLINE> Officer: Moscow to Review Military Ties With U.S., </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, December 21 (Xinhua) -- Russia will review its plan for
military contacts with the U.S. and Britain for next year in light
of the latest events involving Iraq, a senior Russian military
officer said Monday.
</P>
