with legal aspects," he said.
</P>
<P>
He noted that NATO "distanced itself from the action against
Iraq."
</P>
<P>
"The relevant conclusions and corrections will be made by the
Russian military. All maneuvers used against Iraq will be taken
into consideration," he said. 
