(ZCI), the company through which AAC holds shares to safeguard
its interest in ZCCM (Zambia Consolidated Copper Mines), has
concerns in regard to the immediate financial commitment which
would be expected of ZCI at a time when metal prices continue to
decline and ZCI has not been able to attract new partners. In
consequence the board of ZCI has not ratified the memorandum
yet," he said.
</P>
