Sabah (Morning)
</P>
<P>
-- International Monetary Fund's report underlined that Turkey
was mostly affected by the Russian crisis for it has close
commercial ties with Moscow.
</P>
<P>
The report added that Turkey's economic growth will decrease
to 2.9 percent in 1999 from 4.4 percent this year. 
