integration, and new building materials. The investment comes from
Japan, France, Germany, the United States, Belgium, Sweden, and
Switzerland.
</P>
<P>
They enjoy preferential treatment in registration, getting
loans, going through customs procedures, and opening overseas
branches.
</P>
<P>
To date, Beijing area has more than 5,000 high-tech
enterprises.  
